         <abstract>
            <p>The landlord (chaudhri) <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName> of district (pargana) <placeName ref="#dhar">Dhar</placeName> was informed that tax money is due from <placeName ref="#amjhera">Amjhera</placeName> and that a reply 
               to the record-keeper (qanungo) regarding their collection has not been received.</p>
