   <text>
      <body>

         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_pDas_1660_dai_lns235ms_r_r.jpg"/>

         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="per" type="invocation">
            <p>ا</p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div1" xml:id="trans_div1" rend="top centre">
            <p>Alif</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="right margin">
            <p>
               <stamp type="seal" rend="margin (right)"><mentioned>
                     
                  <persName ref="#rafiMuhammad">رفیع محمد</persName>
                  خانه زاد بادشاه 
                  <persName ref="#aurangzebAlamgir">عالمگیر</persName>
                  <num>۶</num>
                  سنه
                  <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">۱۰۷۳</date></mentioned></stamp></p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div2" xml:id="trans_div2">
            <p>
               <stamp type="seal">Round black ink seal<mentioned><gap/> <persName ref="#rafiMuhammad">Rafi Muhammad</persName>, servant of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_badshah">Badshah</ref> <persName ref="#aurangzebAlamgir">Alamgir</persName> in the year 
                  <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">1073</date> [Regnal Year] <date calendar="#julus">6</date></mentioned><note>This seal was issued in 1663–64 CE.</note></stamp>
            </p>
         </div>

         <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="per" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/><persName ref="#purshottamDas">پرسوتمداس</persName>
               چودری
               <placeName ref="#dhar">دهار</placeName>
               را انهاء آنکه مبلغ بابت
               <unclear>باقی</unclear>
               <placeName ref="#amjhera">امجهره</placeName>
               <lb/><unclear>ثابت</unclear>
               رسد قانونگوی دهه
               <unclear>او ست</unclear>
               <persName ref="#muhammadAzim">محمد عاظم</persName>
               را برای تحصیل آن
               <lb/>فرستاده شد ظاهراً جواب محصولی نمیداشت
               <unclear>میداند</unclear>
               تا دام آخر داخل 
               <app><rdg cert="low">سرکار کشد</rdg> <rdg cert="low">کردار کسی</rdg></app>
               <lb/>اگر عرضی
               <unclear>باشد</unclear>
               بحضور آمده ظاهر سازد
               <unclear>و ادا اسواران شدند</unclear>
               <lb/><unclear>بتنخواه حواله باشد</unclear>
               فی جمله که
               درینباب نهایت تاکید دانند
               <lb/>فی التاریخ
               <date calendar="#julus"><num>۲۱</num>
               شهر صفر سنه
               <num>۱۵</num>
               </date>
               جلوس والا
               <g ref="#baiz">بیض</g>
            </p>
         </div>

         <div corresp="#orig_div3" xml:id="trans_div3">
            <p>
               <lb/><persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName>, the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> of <placeName ref="#dhar">Dhar</placeName>, is informed that the amount for the <unclear>arrears</unclear> of <placeName ref="#amjhera">Amjhera</placeName>
               <lb/>was fixed. The <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qanungoi">qanungoi</ref> of village
               <unclear>is his.</unclear>
               <persName ref="#muhammadAzim">Muhammad Azim</persName> has been sent to collect the money.
               <lb/>It is clear that a reply to the request for collection has not been given.
               <unclear>Let it be known</unclear> until the last <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_dam">dam</ref>
               <app><rdg cert="low">shall be entered to the sarkar</rdg><rdg cert="low">the conduct of someone</rdg></app>
               <lb/>If requested, come to the government and make it known.
               <unclear>And the payment of the riders [that] shall be</unclear><!--they shall be the satisfaction/payment/dismissal of the riders? (why is the verb plural?)-->
               <lb/>
               <unclear>shall be assigned to the salary.</unclear>
               Know this matter to be completely settled.
               <lb/>Dated <date calendar="#julus">21 of the month Safar in the year
               15</date>
               of the august reign. <g ref="#baiz">Ended</g>. </p>
         </div>

         <pb n="1v" facs="lf_pDas_1660_dai_lns235ms_r_v.jpg"/>

         <div xml:id="orig_div4" xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" rend="right margin">
            <p>بتاریخ
               <date calendar="#julus"><num>۲۱</num>
               شهر صفر سنه
               <num>۱۵</num></date>
               داخل
               <gap/>
               حضور نموده شد
               <unclear><g ref="#faqt">فقط</g></unclear>
               <lb rend="empty"/>د
            </p>
         </div>

         <div corresp="#orig_div4" xml:id="trans_div4">
            <p>On the date of <date calendar="#julus">21 of the month of Safar in the year
               <num>15</num></date>
               <gap/>
               entered the government
               <unclear><g ref="#faqt">Nothing further.</g></unclear>
               <lb rend="empty"/>[dal]<note>Endorsements on the verso sometimes include single Persian letters below the main inscription. Most common are the letters mim, dal and fe. There is debate over what these letters mean.</note>
            </p>
         </div>
